sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Facade as Facade page<br/>(wippy/facade)
    participant FacadeAPI as /facade/config<br/>(Wippy BE)
    participant Host as Web Host module<br/>(module.js / managed-layout.js)

    Browser->>Facade: GET /
    Facade->>Browser: HTML page with &lt;script src=".../module.js"&gt;
    Browser->>Host: load JS module (registers window.initWippyApp)
    Browser->>FacadeAPI: GET /facade/config
    FacadeAPI->>Browser: AppConfig JSON (auth, env, theming, hostConfig, context)
    Browser->>Host: window.initWippyApp(config, '#app')
    Host->>Host: take over page + browser history, render shell
